          <div id="review_1525312_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1525312_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1682161">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1682161/" class="title-link">税收调查报告</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1682161"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1363797/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1363797-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1363797/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">天地一沙鸥</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar20 main-title-rating" title="较差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-02-12"
      class="main-meta">2009-02-12 13:14:28</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1682161_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  在三联周刊上看到这本书的书评,好象评价很高.而且书评给人的感觉是一本小说.可是看了之后发现是一本调查报告.里面的数字很详实,也访问了村里面的很多人.但是对于不研究社会学的人来说,过于枯燥了.而且书里面重要的内容是在时间轴上记录农村税费改革的变化和影响,读起来有点象流...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1682161/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1682161_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1682161_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3272266">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3272266/" class="title-link">什么叫做经济？</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3272266"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1651821/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1651821/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">deepsea72</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-05-15"
      class="main-meta">2010-05-15 23:11:10</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3272266_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  历史永远都是由无名鼠辈写成的，这个历史唯物主义的基本论断，再次证明不管设计者如何得有如天授，历史总是不断在错误和失败中寻找出口， 政策绝非一刀切的正确，读本书的人需要从财政联想到经济，联系下中国历代基层经济的国、民、地方的发展，以及隐藏的冷冷地利益算计

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3272266_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3272266_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





